name: Sukan Milaye
description:
A relationship without trust is like two people trying to trick the other one into believing something is there that isnt really there. No relationship of any kind can exist without trust…What we are, is our Gift from GOD. And what we become, is our Gift to GOD.A relationship with no trust is like a cell phone with no service, all you can do is play games.
well no matter the distance apart, if you are meant to be together, in the end, you will find yourselves together; if you don’t give up on each other.I don’t care about age difference I am more concern about the heart and i believe so much in chemistry.I am seriously looking for someone i can spend the rest of my life with.am looking for a man that know what he want in life a generous man.Even if you’re far from each other, if your hearts are connected, distance will only be numbers.
